      "raw": "Education\nDoctor of Philosophy (PhD) (ongoing), University of Malaya, Kuala Lumpur, Malaysia.\nMaster of Arts in Malaysian History, University of Malaya, Kuala Lumpur, Malaysia.\nMaster of Arts (MA) in History, University of Dhaka, Dhaka, Bangladesh.\nBachelor of Arts (BA) in History, University of Dhaka, Dhaka, Bangladesh."
