  "publications_raw": [
    "Journal Articles:\nKhondaker\n, M.S.I., Dali, A. M. 2024. Exploring the Nexus: A Study of Malaysia-Bangladesh Relations in the Context of Migrant Workers, 1980-2022. Jebat: Malaysian Journal of History, Politics & Strategic Studies, 51 (2), 218-236.\nhttps://doi.org/10.17576/jebat.2024.5102.05\n(Scopus).\nKhondaker\n, M.S.I., Dali, A. M. 2024. Economic Exchange and Its Constraints in The 20th Century between Malaysia and Bangladesh. Sejarah: Journal of History Department, University of Malaya, 33 (1), 88-116.\nhttps://doi.org/10.22452/sejarah.vol33no1.5\n(Malaysian Citation Index).\nKhondaker\n, M. S. I., & Dali, A. M. (2022). Practice of the Muslim Brotherhood between Malaysia And Bangladesh.\nMalaysian Journal of Islamic Sciences\n,\n34\n(1), 1-15. Retrieved from\nhttps://uijournal.usim.edu.my/index.php/uij/article/view/376\n, (Peer reviewed).\nKhondaker,\nM. S. I. 2022. “Tun Mahathir's administration of Malaysia's relationship with Bangladesh: A preliminary appraisal”\nReligación: Journal of Social Sciences and Humanities,\nVol. 6, No. 30: 1-18 (Peer-reviewed).\nAkhtar, S. Idris, H. and\nM Shahidul Islam Khondaker.\n2022. “Tracing Trade Connection between Ancient Entrepot Kedah and Tamralipti Reference to An Archaeological and A Literary Evidence,”\nJournal of the Malaysian Museum Association,\nVol.41 (Peer-reviewed).\nAkhtar, Sharmin, and\nM Shahidul Islam Khondaker.\n2021. “Early Life Leadership Dimensions of Sheikh Mujibur Rahman: An Exceptional Political Leadership Model”.\nJournal of Humanities and Social Sciences Studies,\nNo. 3 (5):01-09. (Peer-reviewed).\nAkhtar, Sharmin and\nM Shahidul Islam Khondaker.\n2021. “Mapping Bengal’s factors and Indianization of Southeast Asia”,\nJournal of Arts and Humanities (JAH),\nVol. 10, No. 01:19-30. (Peer reviewed).\nKhondaker. M.S.I.\n& Akhtar, S. 2025. “Ancient Pottery Artisanship of Bukit Tengkorak (Sabah): An Unpretentious Bornean Tradition,” Malaysia Museums Journal (in press).",
